        "subject": "LU-10149 tests: avoid live-lock with concurrent memsets",
        "message": "LU-10149 tests: avoid live-lock with concurrent memsets\n\nThis patch splits and delays concurrents memsets to reduce the\nexecution time of auto-tests using mmap_sanity, due to some\npossible live-lock situation likely to occur in mmap_tst[3,4]\nsub-tests.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I94d11e8423304ebfcd435c751f8e2fdd1cafd525\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
